# ================= PATH / STORAGE =================
# Lokasi folder data (db lokal + cdn lokal).
# Biarkan kosong untuk auto-detect:
#   • VPS          → <app_root>/data  (otomatis)
#   • Pterodactyl  → /home/container/data  (otomatis, deteksi via P_SERVER_UUID)
#   • Vercel       → /tmp/data  (otomatis, read-only fs)
# Isi manual hanya jika kamu ingin override lokasi custom:
# DATA_DIR=/home/container/data

# ================= CDN =================
